# Copy to apps/backend/.dev.vars (gitignored) for local `wrangler dev`.
# Production/staging secrets are set with `wrangler secret put` (YK-487).
# Server-side ONLY — never shipped to the client bundle.
#
# Privy (App ID is public, but the SECRET lives here, never EXPO_PUBLIC_*):
# PRIVY_APP_ID=
# PRIVY_APP_SECRET=
#
# DATABASE_URL=   (Neon via Hyperdrive — YK-487)
